Class SortByBrewery

  • java.lang.Object
    • beer_garden_rscs.SortByBrewery

  • public class SortByBrewery
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to sort each beer into a list who's index allows for easy reference to a brewery's name, location and logo. This allows for the creation of brewery tables and lists in the Beer Buddy database.

    treyhowie

      • sortBeersByBrewery

        public static void sortBeersByBrewery()
        This subroutine sorts all the beers found on the Tap Hunter site, by BeerInformationScavenger.gatherBeerInformation() by their respective breweries. This is used for adding new brewery tables to the Beer Buddy database in the DatabasePopulation class.
